---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="TrustMeBro Privacy Policy - How we handle your data (spoiler: we're not creepy about it)">
  <Header />
  
  <main class="min-h-screen pt-8 pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-4">
          <span class="gradient-text">Privacy</span> Policy
        </h1>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg">the boring but important stuff 🔒</p>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-2">Last updated: November 30, 2025</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="prose max-w-none space-y-8">
        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold gradient-text mb-4">TL;DR (Summary) ⚡</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300">
            <li>• We collect minimal data (just what's needed to run the site)</li>
            <li>• We don't sell your info to anyone</li>
            <li>• We use cookies for basic analytics and ads</li>
            <li>• You can contact us anytime about your data</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold gradient-text mb-4">1. Information We Collect 📊</h2>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-purple-400">Automatically Collected</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">When you visit TrustMeBro, we automatically collect:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-400 mb-4">
            <li>• Browser type and version</li>
            <li>• Device type (mobile, desktop, etc.)</li>
            <li>• Pages you visit and time spent</li>
            <li>• Referring website</li>
            <li>• Approximate location (country/city level)</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-purple-400">Information You Provide</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-400">
            <li>• Email address (if you subscribe to newsletter)</li>
            <li>• Contact form submissions</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold gradient-text mb-4">2. How We Use Your Info 🎯</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300">
            <li>• To improve our website and content</li>
            <li>• To send newsletters (only if you signed up)</li>
            <li>• To respond to your messages</li>
            <li>• To show relevant ads (we gotta keep the lights on)</li>
            <li>• To analyze traffic and trends</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold gradient-text mb-4">3. Cookies 🍪</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
            Yeah, we use cookies. Not the delicious kind, unfortunately. These are small files 
            that help us understand how you use our site.
          </p>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-purple-400">Types of Cookies We Use:</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-400">
            <li>• <strong>Essential:</strong> Required for the site to work</li>
            <li>• <strong>Analytics:</strong> Help us understand traffic (Google Analytics)</li>
            <li>• <strong>Advertising:</strong> Used to show relevant ads (Google AdSense)</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4 text-sm">
            You can disable cookies in your browser settings, but some features might not work properly.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold gradient-text mb-4">4. Third-Party Services 🔗</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">We use some third-party services:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-400">
            <li>• <strong>Google Analytics:</strong> For website analytics</li>
            <li>• <strong>Google AdSense:</strong> For displaying ads</li>
            <li>• <strong>Netlify:</strong> For hosting our website</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4 text-sm">
            These services have their own privacy policies. We recommend checking them out.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold gradient-text mb-4">5. Your Rights 💪</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">You have the right to:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-400">
            <li>• Access your personal data</li>
            <li>• Request deletion of your data</li>
            <li>• Opt-out of marketing emails</li>
            <li>• Disable cookies</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4">
            To exercise these rights, email us at: 
            <a href="mailto:privacy@trustmebro.pro" class="text-cyan-400 hover:underline">privacy@trustmebro.pro</a>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold gradient-text mb-4">6. Data Security 🔐</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            We take reasonable measures to protect your information. Our site uses HTTPS, 
            and we don't store sensitive data. But no system is 100% secure, so we can't 
            guarantee absolute security (no one can, tbh).
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold gradient-text mb-4">7. Children's Privacy 👶</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            TrustMeBro is not intended for children under 13. We don't knowingly collect 
            information from children. If you're a parent and think your child has provided 
            us with personal info, please contact us.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold gradient-text mb-4">8. Changes to This Policy 📝</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            We might update this policy occasionally. When we do, we'll update the "Last updated" 
            date at the top. Major changes will be announced on our site.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold gradient-text mb-4">9. Contact Us 📬</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            Questions about this privacy policy? Hit us up:
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-gray-400">
            <li>Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@trustmebro.pro" class="text-cyan-400 hover:underline">privacy@trustmebro.pro</a></li>
            <li>Contact Form: <a href="/contact" class="text-cyan-400 hover:underline">trustmebro.pro/contact</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
